<subSubSection pageId="78" pageNumber="79" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="78.[151,1436,257,606]" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,437,462]" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">Remarks.</emphasis>
Name introduced to distinguish 
<taxonomicName authority="Brocchi, 1814" authorityName="Brocchi" authorityYear="1814" box="[680,1044,437,462]" class="Gastropoda" family="Gastropoda (awaiting allocation)" genus="Anomia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Gastropoda (awaiting allocation)" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="striata">
<emphasis box="[680,857,438,461]" italics="true" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">Anomia striata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation box="[873,1044,437,462]" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" refId="ref81158" refString="Brocchi, G. B. (1814) Conchiologia fossile subapennina con osservazioni geologiche sugli Apennini e sul suolo adiacente. 2 Vols. Stamperia Reale, Milano, 56 + 80 [Roman numerals] + 712 pp., 16 pls." type="book">Brocchi, 1814</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, sensu 
<bibRefCitation box="[1143,1375,437,462]" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" refId="ref86070" refString="Loven, S. L. (1846). Nordens Hafs - Mollusker. Index Molluscorum litora Scandinaviae occidentalia habitantium. Ofversigt af Kongliga Vetenskaps Akademiens Forhandlingar, 1846, 134 - 160, 182 - 204. [Offprint, pp. 1 - 50]" type="journal article">Lovén (1846: 183)</bibRefCitation>
, and accompanied by a description. 
<taxonomicName box="[507,665,473,498]" class="Bivalvia" family="Anomiidae" genus="Monia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pterioida" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="glauca">
<emphasis box="[507,665,473,498]" italics="true" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">Monia glauca</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was considered as valid by 
<bibRefCitation box="[992,1212,473,498]" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" refId="ref88677" refString="Sabelli, B., Giannuzzi-Savelli, R. &amp; Bedulli, D. (1990 - 1992) Catalogo Annotato dei Molluschi Marini del Mediterraneo- Annotated Check-List of the Mediterranean Marine Mollusks. 3 Vols. Edizioni Libreria Naturalistica Bolognese, Bologna, xiv + 781 pp." type="book">
Sabelli 
<emphasis box="[1079,1138,473,498]" italics="true" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">et al.</emphasis>
(
<date box="[1154,1212,473,497]" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" value="1990" valueMax="1992">1990</date>
</bibRefCitation>
–1992: 84, 296—as 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Monterosato" baseAuthorityYear="1884" box="[151,388,509,534]" class="Bivalvia" family="Anomiidae" genus="Pododesmus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pterioida" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="glaucus">
<emphasis box="[151,388,509,534]" italics="true" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">Pododesmus glaucus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), and is recorded as a possible synonym of 
<emphasis box="[891,1128,509,534]" italics="true" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Philippi" authorityYear="1837" box="[891,1032,509,534]" class="Bivalvia" family="Anomiidae" genus="Pododesmus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pterioida" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">Pododesmus</taxonomicName>
squama
</emphasis>
(Gmelin, 1791) which is a valid species (
<bibRefCitation box="[310,472,545,570]" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" refId="ref85090" refString="Holmes, A. M. (2017) Phylogenetics of British saddle oysters (Bivalvia: Anomiidae) - A review of the shell morphology, internal anatomy and genetics of Pododesmus in British waters. Journal of Conchology, 42 (5), 317 - 325." type="journal article">Holmes, 2017</bibRefCitation>
) by MolluscaBase (2018). We keep it under this synonymy, although it may be rather related to 
<taxonomicName authority="(Linnaeus, 1761)" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1761" baseAuthorityName="Linnaeus" baseAuthorityYear="1761" box="[263,756,581,606]" class="Bivalvia" family="Anomiidae" genus="Pododesmus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Pterioida" pageId="78" pageNumber="79" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="patelliformis">
<emphasis box="[263,554,581,606]" italics="true" pageId="78" pageNumber="79">Pododesmus patelliformis</emphasis>
(Linnaeus, 1761)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
